# Organization Token Mapping
#
# Format: organization_name=api_token
#
# Example:
# org1=AbCdEf123456789
# org2=XyZ987654321abc
#
# Usage:
#   cp org.txt.example org.txt
#   Edit org.txt with your organization names and tokens
#   Run: ./org-migration.sh --organization org1 migrate -r organizations

# Add your organizations below
# org1=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
# org2=YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
